Class InvocationCommandException

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • com.sk89q.intake.CommandException
          • com.sk89q.intake.InvocationCommandException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class InvocationCommandException
extends CommandException
    Thrown when invocation of a command fails, wrapping the exception that is thrown.

    Throwable.getCause() will not be null.
